                           </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">This book is of<name ref="PRS12407WaldaAragawi">Walda ʾAragāwi</name> who let it be written and acquired it with his money.
                              Whoever erased it and stole it, be excommunicated through the power of the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit, <name ref="PRS2033AriusA">Arius</name>.
                             </q>
                           <note>How the cataloguer reconstructed the name of the owner, is unclear.</note>
                        </item>
